      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 62 六二</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 62 六二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六二：過其祖，遇其妣；不及其君，遇其臣；无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second SIX, divided, shows its subject passing by his grandfather, and meeting with his grandmother; not attempting anything against his ruler, but meeting him as his minister. There will be no error.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
