      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 62 九三</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 62 九三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九三：弗過防之，從或戕之，凶。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third NINE, undivided, shows its subject taking no extraordinary precautions against danger; and some in consequence finding opportunity to assail and injure him. There will be evil.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
