      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 62 九四</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 62 九四</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九四：无咎，弗過遇之。往厲必戒，勿用永貞。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth NINE, undivided, shows its subject falling into no error, but meeting (the exigency of his situation), without exceeding (in his natural. course). If he go forward, there will be peril, and he must be cautious. There is no occasion to be using firmness perpetually.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
