      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 62 六五</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 62 六五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六五：密云不雨，自我西郊，公弋取彼在穴。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth SIX, divided, (suggests the idea) of dense clouds, but no rain, coming from our borders in the west. It also (shows) the prince shooting his arrow, and taking the bird in a cave.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
